The life of a phone is fleeting, and often the end comes without warning. One minute your device is at 20 percent power, and before you can say “bag of rice,” you’re at 1 percent. And with the recent news that source code from Apple’s iOS mobile operating system had been leaked, potentially giving hackers the opportunity to exploit weaknesses, the world is a more dangerous place for your phone than ever before. College Humor created this perfect slice-of-life sketch about the tragic and always untimely death of your phone. Unfortunately, it’s something we’ll all have to face one day.